gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留兩個言連少少貢獻都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲閪女人就係咁，又口多又冇建設性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做男人做到你咁垃圾 少少積蓄都無仲咁大聲<br />\n8年啦 我隻狗3年都特登儲開一筆錢係比佢備用<br />\n都預留咗幾皮比佢有咩急事用啦<br />\n我一年前夠辭咗工 唔好講到辭咗工好可憐啦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"八年前仲係中學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知你想點，個post 講蛇你又講你隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識就走唔好搞事啦<br />\n狗就話拖住抱住攞出街啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通我攞住條蛇出街咩？太光太嘈會嚇親佢你知唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"咁你由佢病囉 講就講咗 你硬係要駁都無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗真係見到你喺度推推推<br />\n我又唔覺得呢個post有好多人幫到你呀<br />\n你話你嗰隻係貓 就會好多人幫你<br />\n叫你搵獸醫睇 無錢<br />\n又鬧人無貢獻 起碼check咗知咩事<br />\n就算基本診金都比咗先 又攞唔出 定唔願攞 唔清楚<br />\n醫生講咩 你再update上嚟 你可以決定唔喺獸醫度醫 但起碼會有人建議你點做先！<br />\n又要話人哋唔識 又話驚嚇親佢 咁多藉口<br />\n同埋 關我隻狗咩事？蛇同狗 就唔係寵物咩？<br />\n無論係咪屬於同一種類 有病就係要醫<br />\n而家係屌緊你咁大個人少少積蓄都無<br />\n我自己都係做咗兩三年嘢 都有幾皮係for寵物用<br />\n我就係知佢哋有咩事都要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你真係寧願死馬當活馬醫 都唔願用多少少錢睇醫生？<br />\n所以我第一個留言已經講 萬一比你想像嚴重咁點算"},{"pid":"c64d9f00c1fd4b5875d6d276ed48c547efe37676","tid":1259941,"uid":245290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"上網search  <br />\n有d似Scale Rot<br />\n但你條蛇好似深色d 似血色<br />\n利伸：我都好窮，好驚d龜會病 <br />\n如果真係病左，應該會借錢睇落去 <br />\n最多之後慢慢還 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reptile-savvy.weebly.com/scaleshell-rot.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freptile-savvy.weebly.com%2Fscaleshell-rot.html&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkruaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=226b2fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://reptile-savvy.weebly.com/scaleshell-rot.html</a><br />\nScale Rot  is a colloquial term for a range of conditions affecting the skin of reptiles which results in severe infection.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4mYsKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4mYsKx.jpg&h=c6b51469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBlister Disease &ndash; This form of scale rot is often seen in snakes, particularly semi-aquatic species such as garter or water snakes. It can however occur in any species which are exposed to a persistently damp substrate or soiled substrate. The outer layer of skin develops blisters which becomes secondarily infected with environmental bacteria. These can progress to envelop the whole of the ventral area of the snake and lead to septicaemia. Occasionally this may be caused be fungus rather than bacteria."},{"pid":"14259687807bbc860cb68ca01c3c85ccd8c2d512","tid":1259941,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c64d9f00c1fd4b5875d6d276ed48c547efe37676","tid":1259941,"uid":245290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"上網search  <br />\n有d似Scale Rot<br />\n但你條蛇好似深色d 似血色<br />\n利伸：我都好窮，好驚d龜會病 <br />\n如果真係病左，應該會借錢睇落去 <br />\n最多之後慢慢還 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://reptile-savvy.weebly.com/scaleshell-rot.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freptile-savvy.weebly.com%2Fscaleshell-rot.html&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkruaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=226b2fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://reptile-savvy.weebly.com/scaleshell-rot.html</a><br />\nScale Rot  is a colloquial term for a range of conditions affecting the skin of reptiles which results in severe infection.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4mYsKx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c